  "prompt": "Where is a reliable mobile repair shop to get my phone screen replaced in Kolkata?",
  "response": "In Kolkata, there are several reliable mobile repair shops where you can get your phone screen replaced. Here are a few highly recommended options:\n\n1. **iPlanet Service Center**\n   - **Location:** Multiple locations, including Sector V and Park Street\n   - **Why Choose:** Known for quick service and using genuine parts. They handle repairs for various brands.\n\n2. **Symphony Service Center**\n   - **Location:** 7A, Bentinck Street, 1st Floor, Kolkata - 700001\n   - **Why Choose:** They have a good reputation for quality service and are authorized service centers for multiple brands.\n\n3. **Fix My Gadget**\n   - **Location:** 11/1A, Sarat Bose Road, Kolkata - 700020\n   - **Why Choose:** A specialized service center known for professional service and reasonable pricing.\n\n4. **M.Service Solutions**\n   - **Location:** 119, Park Street, 3rd Floor, Kolkata - 700016\n   - **Why Choose:** They provide doorstep services and have a good track record of customer satisfaction.\n\nBefore visiting, it's always a good idea to call and confirm if they have the necessary parts in stock for your specific phone model. Also, inquire about the warranty on the repair work to ensure peace of mind.",
